}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleswftXXarrow}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Delta  \vdash  \ottnt{A}}%
\ottpremise{\Delta  \vdash  \ottnt{B}}%
}{

\newcommand{\ottdruleswftXXall}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

{\ottdrulename{swft\_all}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleswftXXand}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

}{

\newcommand{\ottdruleSXXand}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

}{
[\cdot]  \ottsym{:}  \ottsym{(}  \Delta  \ottsym{;}  \Gamma \, \Rightarrow \, \ottnt{A}  \ottsym{)}  \mapsto  \ottsym{(}  \Delta  \ottsym{;}  \Gamma \, \Rightarrow \, \ottnt{A}  \ottsym{)}  \rightsquigarrow  [\cdot]}{%
{\ottdrulename{CTyp\_empty1}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleCTypXXemptyTwo}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{

{\ottdrulename{CTyp\_empty2}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleCTypXXappLOne}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\mathcal{C}  \ottsym{:}  \ottsym{(}  \Delta  \ottsym{;}  \Gamma \, \Rightarrow \, \ottnt{A}  \ottsym{)}  \mapsto  \ottsym{(}  \Delta'  \ottsym{;}  \Gamma' \, \Rightarrow \, \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \rightarrow  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \ottsym{)}  \rightsquigarrow  \mathcal{D}}%
\ottpremise{ \Delta'  ;  \Gamma'    \vdash    \mathit{E}_{{\mathrm{2}}}    \Leftarrow   \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   \ottnt{e} } }%
}{
\mathcal{C} \, \mathit{E}_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \ottsym{:}  \ottsym{(}  \Delta  \ottsym{;}  \Gamma \, \Rightarrow \, \ottnt{A}  \ottsym{)}  \mapsto  \ottsym{(}  \Delta'  \ottsym{;}  \Gamma' \, \Rightarrow \, \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \ottsym{)}  \rightsquigarrow  \mathcal{D} \, \ottnt{e}}{%
{\ottdrulename{CTyp\_appL1}}{}%
}}

\newcommand{\ottdruleCTypXXabsOne}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\newcommand{\ottdruleCTypXXtabsOne}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\newcommand{\ottdruleAXXand}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{ \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co_{{\mathrm{1}}} } }%
\ottpremise{ \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co_{{\mathrm{2}}} } }%
}{
 \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \, \& \,  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow     \llbracket  \mathcal{Q}  \rrbracket^{\&}   \circ  \langle  co_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \ottsym{,}  co_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \rangle  } }{%
{\ottdrulename{A\_and}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleAXXrcdConst}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{ \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:  c  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co } }%
}{
  \ottmv{l}  ,  \mathcal{Q}    \vdash   \ottsym{\{}  \ottmv{l}  \ottsym{:}  \ottnt{A}  \ottsym{\}}  <:  c  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co } }{%
{\ottdrulename{A\_rcdConst}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleAXXrcd}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{  \mathcal{Q}  ,  \ottmv{l}    \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottnt{B}  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co } }%
}{
 \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottsym{\{}  \ottmv{l}  \ottsym{:}  \ottnt{B}  \ottsym{\}}  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co } }{%
{\ottdrulename{A\_rcd}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleAXXarr}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{  \mathcal{Q}  ,  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{1}}}}    \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co } }%
}{
 \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \rightarrow  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co } }{%
{\ottdrulename{A\_arr}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleAXXforall}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{  \mathcal{Q}  ,  \alpha  *  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{1}}}}    \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co } }%
}{
 \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:   \forall (  \alpha   *   \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  ) .\, \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{2}}}}   \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co } }{%
{\ottdrulename{A\_forall}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleAXXandConst}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{ \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A_{\ottmv{i}}}  <:  c  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co } }%
\ottpremise{ i \in \{ 1, 2 \} }%
}{
 \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \, \& \,  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  <:  c  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow    co  \circ   \pi_i   } }{%
{\ottdrulename{A\_andConst}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleAXXarrConst}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{ \ottsym{[]}   \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co_{{\mathrm{1}}} } }%
\ottpremise{ \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  <:  c  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co_{{\mathrm{2}}} } }%
}{
  \ottnt{A}  ,  \mathcal{Q}    \vdash   \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \rightarrow  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  <:  c  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  co_{{\mathrm{2}}} } }{%
{\ottdrulename{A\_arrConst}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruleAXXallConst}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\ottsym{[]}  \vdash  \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}}%
\ottpremise{ \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  <:  c  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co } }%
}{
 \ottsym{(}   \alpha  *  \ottnt{A}  ,  \mathcal{Q}   \ottsym{)}   \vdash    \forall (  \alpha   *   \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  ) .\, \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}   <:  c  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow    co _{\forall}  } }{%
{\ottdrulename{A\_allConst}}{}%
}}

\newcommand{\ottdefnASub}[1]{\begin{ottdefnblock}[#1]{$ \mathcal{Q}   \vdash   \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottnt{B}  \rulehl{ \rightsquigarrow   co } $}{}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleAXXconst{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleAXXtop{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleAXXbot{}}

\ottusedrule{\ottdruleAXXrcd{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleAXXarr{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleAXXforall{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdruleAXXandConst{}}

\newcommand{\ottdrulectXXtrans}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\newcommand{\ottdrulectXXarr}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

}{
 co_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  co_{{\mathrm{2}}}  ::  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}   \triangleright   \tau'_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  \tau'_{{\mathrm{2}}} }{%

\newcommand{\ottdrulectXXpair}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\ottpremise{ co_{{\mathrm{2}}}  ::  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}   \triangleright   \tau_{{\mathrm{3}}} }%

 \langle  co_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \ottsym{,}  co_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \rangle  ::  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}   \triangleright   \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \times  \tau_{{\mathrm{3}}} }{%
{\ottdrulename{ct\_pair}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulectXXdistArr}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
}{
 \mathsf{dist}_{\rightarrow}  ::  \ottsym{(}  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \ottsym{)}  \times  \ottsym{(}  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  \tau_{{\mathrm{3}}}  \ottsym{)}   \triangleright   \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}  \times  \tau_{{\mathrm{3}}} }{%
{\ottdrulename{ct\_distArr}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulectXXdistAll}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

 \mathsf{dist}_{\forall}  ::  \ottsym{(}   \forall  \alpha .\, \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}   \ottsym{)}  \times  \ottsym{(}   \forall  \alpha .\, \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}   \ottsym{)}   \triangleright    \forall  \alpha .\, \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \times  \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}  }{%

}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulectXXprojl}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\newcommand{\ottdrulectXXprojr}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

{\ottdrulename{ct\_projr}}{}%

\newcommand{\ottdrulectXXforall}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\newcommand{\ottdrulectXXtopAll}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\newcommand{\ottdruletXXunit}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Phi  \vdash  \Psi}%
}{
\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \langle \rangle  \ottsym{:}  \langle \rangle}{%
{\ottdrulename{t\_unit}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruletXXnat}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

}{
\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  i  \ottsym{:}  \mathsf{Int}}{%
{\ottdrulename{t\_nat}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruletXXvar}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Phi  \vdash  \Psi}%
\ottpremise{ (  \ottmv{x}  :  \tau  ) \in  \Psi }%
}{
\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{:}  \tau}{%
{\ottdrulename{t\_var}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruletXXabs}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \ottsym{,}  \ottmv{x}  \ottsym{:}  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \vdash  \ottnt{e}  \ottsym{:}  \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}}%
\ottpremise{\Phi  \vdash  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}}%
}{
\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash   \lambda \ottmv{x} .\, \ottnt{e}   \ottsym{:}  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}}{%
{\ottdrulename{t\_abs}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruletXXapp}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \ottsym{:}  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \rightarrow  \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}}%
\ottpremise{\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \ottsym{:}  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}}%
}{
\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{1}}}} \, \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \ottsym{:}  \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}}{%
{\ottdrulename{t\_app}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruletXXpair}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \ottsym{:}  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}}%
\ottpremise{\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \ottsym{:}  \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}}%
}{
\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \langle  \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  \ottsym{,}  \ottnt{e_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \rangle  \ottsym{:}  \tau_{{\mathrm{1}}}  \times  \tau_{{\mathrm{2}}}}{%
{\ottdrulename{t\_pair}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruletXXtabs}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Phi  \ottsym{,}  \alpha  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \ottnt{e}  \ottsym{:}  \tau}%
\ottpremise{\Phi  \vdash  \Psi}%
}{
\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash   \Lambda  \alpha .\, \ottnt{e}   \ottsym{:}   \forall  \alpha .\, \tau }{%
{\ottdrulename{t\_tabs}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruletXXtapp}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \ottnt{e}  \ottsym{:}   \forall  \alpha .\, \tau' }%

\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \ottnt{e} \, \tau  \ottsym{:}   [  \tau  /  \alpha  ]  \tau' }{%
{\ottdrulename{t\_tapp}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdruletXXcapp}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%

\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  co \, \ottnt{e}  \ottsym{:}  \tau'}{%
{\ottdrulename{t\_capp}}{}%
}}

\newcommand{\ottdefntyp}[1]{\begin{ottdefnblock}[#1]{$\Phi  \ottsym{;}  \Psi  \vdash  \ottnt{e}  \ottsym{:}  \tau$}{}

\newcommand{\ottdrulefsubXXforall}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Delta  \vdash  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  <:  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}}%
\ottpremise{\Delta  \ottsym{,}  \alpha  <:  \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  \vdash  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  <:  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}%
}{
\Delta  \vdash   \forall (  \alpha   <:   \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  ) .\,  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{1}}}}   <:   \forall (  \alpha   <:   \ottnt{A_{{\mathrm{2}}}}  ) .\,  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{2}}}} }{%
{\ottdrulename{fsub\_forall}}{}%
}}


\newcommand{\ottdrulefsubXXforallw}[1]{\ottdrule[#1]{%
\ottpremise{\Delta  \ottsym{,}  \alpha  <:  \ottnt{A}  \vdash  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{1}}}}  <:  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{2}}}}}%
}{
\Delta  \vdash   \forall (  \alpha   <:   \ottnt{A}  ) .\,  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{1}}}}   <:   \forall (  \alpha   <:   \ottnt{A}  ) .\,  \ottnt{B_{{\mathrm{2}}}} }{%
{\ottdrulename{fsub\_forallw}}{}%
}}

\newcommand{\ottdefnfsub}[1]{\begin{ottdefnblock}[#1]{$\Delta  \vdash  \ottnt{A}  <:  \ottnt{B}$}{}
\ottusedrule{\ottdrulefsubXXforall{}}
\ottusedrule{\ottdrulefsubXXforallw{}}
\end{ottdefnblock}}


\newcommand{\ottdefnsFS}{
\ottdefnfsub{}}

}
